//   - Typed convenience methods on *ClientWithResponses
//   - Sentinel errors ErrNotFound and ErrUnsupportedApp
//
// Regenerate with: make gen-client (requires oapi-codegen in PATH).
// The generated file is committed so go build works without a live backend.
